EASEL ON


          Account Relationship Code (Incentive) - Help

    Used to define how the Related Balance Category Codes
    1 & 2 on MICM 7102 (Product Definition) will be used to
    qualify a relationship for incentives.  Valid entries are:

      A  All related accounts must meet the individual balance
         requirement. If one account fails, the relationship
         fails.
      O  A minimum of one related account must meet the
         individual balance requirement to qualify for
         incentives.
                                                                _
